When I complete a task it shows up in my activity stream as simply having updated the wiki page that the task is on. It should show as a custom event, task completion and it should mention the task summary rather than just the page name. I want to be able to see in the activity stream for any given users which tasks they completed and when.

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
